<div class="alert alert-info" i18n:domain="novaideo">
   <p i18n:translate="">
     The writing system is based on the variables to allow the adaptation of the message to send to the subscribers of the newsletter. The variables are:
   </p>
   <ul>
   	<li><strong>{first_name}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">The subscriber's first name,</span></li>
   	<li><strong>{last_name}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">The subscriber's last name,</span></li>
   	<li><strong>{application_title}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">The application's title,</span></li>
   	<li><strong>{application_url}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">The application's URL,</span></li>
   	<li><strong>{logo}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">The logo's URL,</span></li>
   	<li><strong>{newsletter_title}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">The newsletter's title,</span></li>
   	<li><strong>{unsubscribeurl}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">Unsubscribe URL,</span></li>
   	<li><strong>{content}:</strong> <span i18n:translate="">Content automatically generated according to subscribers' preferences. The generate text contains the recently published ideas and proposals.</span></li>
   </ul>
   <p i18n:translate="">
     You can use these variables for the subject or body of your newsletter.
   </p>
</div>